projectGridLines.description:
Project 1

Title: Coin feature

Description: Students will be making a project to improve our Solana wallets

Skill sets: Typescript, Nodejs, Mongodb, NextJS

Traits expectation: Git knowledge, Debugging, problem solving, Good communication, Coordination with teams in different geographies

Expected learning: Rolling out a feature in the production environment

Specific courses required for project execution: Computer Science
